description: What an amazing opportunity to bring two superstars together for one awesome electrifying scene. Colton Grey, is a Bible thumping good doer who knocks on the wrong door, or maybe the right door, of Pheonix Fellington. After a little small talk Pheonix knows exactly what to do and the two men literally try to suck the sin out of each other before engaging in an all-out sinful fuck fest. Hallelujah.
title: He Will Save Us All
